---
import WorkDetail from '@pt/layouts/WorkDetail.astro'
---

<WorkDetail
  title="FullFill"
  company="Tashi"
  period="2021 – 2022"
  role="QA Analyst"
  category="Health & Wellness · iOS & Android"
  stack={['React Native', 'QA', 'iOS & Android']}
>
  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-[#c9873a] uppercase">Overview</p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] font-light text-white/60">
      FullFill is a health and wellness app built with React Native for iOS and Android. The app is designed to help
      users build meaningful habits and track their wellness journey in a structured, motivating way.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-[#c9873a] uppercase">My Role</p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-[15px] leading-[1.9] font-light text-white/60">
      As a QA Analyst at Tashi, I was responsible for the full test process — making sure every release was organized,
      trackable, and met quality standards before reaching users.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a]"></span><p
          class="text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-white/50"
        >
          Organized and managed test processes across development and release cycles.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a]"></span><p
          class="text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-white/50"
        >
          Kept track of test cases, results, and defects to ensure full visibility across the team.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a]"></span><p
          class="text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-white/50"
        >
          Worked closely with developers to identify, report, and verify bug fixes before release.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</WorkDetail>
